subject: College Athletics
Basketball
lead_paragraph: Ashton Gibbs had 21 points, and No. 19 Pittsburgh dealt No. 3 Villanova its second straight loss in their first meeting since Villanova’s dramatic N.C.A.A. tournament victory last season.
